    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car that still looks great on the road. It drives smoothly and has been well-loved, so it's ready for its next big adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
