    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending torque through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. This example has undergone essential preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS solenoid overhaul. The chassis remains taut with responsive steering rack feedback, and the suspension geometry is dialed for spirited driving. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its age, the drivetrain integrity is paramount. A robust, enthusiast-maintained driver\u2019s car ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 13
    },
    {
