      "description": "This 2017 Porsche Macan S is a meticulously maintained example of precision engineering. Finished in a deep Volcano Grey Metallic, the exterior retains a brilliant shine, showing only minor road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the black leather interior remains supple and smoke-free, with all electronic features and dual-zone climate controls functioning perfectly. It has been garage-kept and serviced exclusively at authorized centers, with a complete log of recent oil changes and brake inspections. The 3.0L V6 biturbo engine delivers a smooth, responsive power band, and the PDK transmission shifts with crisp accuracy. It sits on well-treaded performance tires and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
